reviews: Holds my iron and my solder spool securely and conveniently.

Well, to be perfectly honest, as we haven’t suffered a flood or a house fire since receiving this bag, I’m rather taking it’s effectiveness on trust.

Seriously though, it is obviously very well made from some seriously businesslike materials so I am expecting that it will protect our documents and small valuables as it is supposed to.

The size is great too. All of our personal documentation fits without any need for folding any of it.

Fit a made in USA J bass without issue.
Looks great too.

Using this power bar as a master supply and switch for our garden / patio lighting. The long cord made it super easy to locate it where it was the most convenient without having to mess around with additional extension cords etc. Works great and the supplied wall mounting hardware is easy to use and very sturdy.

review_title: A nice upgrade for an oddball project!
reviews: I used these to replace the worn out and crumbling caster wheels on an old guitar speaker cabinet. The original casters had an unusual base plate size by today’s standards so a drop-in replacement assembly seemed to be a tall order. With these wheels installed into the original casters, the cabinet is rolling freely once more. An added bonus is just how quiet these are when rolling on hard surfaces.
Used this to replace one of those fantastically infuriating anti-flood hoses that would continually shut itself down during normal use. This hose is working fabulously and was a breeze to install.

My teenage daughter loves these toques! Collecting all of the colour options, it would seem.
Well made and comfortable.

I’ve used these protectors on other phones for our family with great success and these are no exception. Arguably the most effective installation guide / jig makes fitting these a breeze and professional results are readily attainable. Highly recommended.

review_title: Great product at a great price.
reviews: I have used these protectors on other phones over the years. Their installation kit makes professional-grade results easy and the product works! :)
An absolute wealth of knowledge presented in a refreshing and enlightening manner.

I’ve always preferred copper over aluminum. It blocks far more rf and you can solder to it. The conductive adhesive works well but I do add a touch of solder at joins to ensure that a solid, continuous Faraday ‘cage’ is created. It’s not necessary but it satisfies my ocd tendencies!

review_title: Fits my old poles a treat.
reviews:
Bought this to replace the original one that came with my hiking poles that I misplaced.
Fits great and makes storing them in my vehicle that much tidier.

One of our dogs is a bit of a Steve McQueen-esque escape artist. This makes keeping a window open a decent amount (especially when parking) for the dogs so much easier and worry free. It does add some wind noise when driving but that’s a minor inconvenience in comparison.
Bought these to help install one of the fan-style led lights into a recessed pot light fitting. Did the trick beautifully.

Bought this in the hope that it might brighten up one poorly lit area in my basement workshop. It works fantastically well!!! No more needing the flashlight on my phone to see into toolbox drawers for me!!!
Using this in my vehicle which, for whatever reason, seems to be a charging cable graveyard. A couple of weeks of use so far and this cable is surviving well.
I’ve been buying and wearing Merrells for some years now. These were exactly what I am used to but at a much better price than regular retail stores.
Comfy, warm and stylish. (As reviewed by both my wife and my teenaged daughter - who are the actual recipients!)

This snake is heavy and cumbersome but does get the job done. The “crank handle” is next to useless unless you snap a pair of vice grips onto it. The angle of deviation between the two spinning grips is so minimal that there is zero leverage available as is.

The screen protectors are very good...the guide frame not so much as the protectors don’t pass through it cleanly. Found that it was ok assuming that you didn’t snap the guide onto the phone at both ends. That way you can start the protector at the snapped on end and pull the guide out of the way as you lower the rest of the protector to the screen. I did waste one protector figuring that out but, at this price, I’m still happy with the product.
I didn’t actually order this book but I do own it having bought it back in the 90’s! So, I can attest to it being full of good, accurate transcriptions. :)
Our three 20lb-ish dogs love these...they definitely consider them to be a special treat compared to other ‘snacks’ that we give them.
Super easy to install and set up. Instructions were very clear and well laid out. We have a three wire heat / cooling set up. This thermostat is working great with our older model gas furnace.
Very decent quality for such an affordable patch cable set. Needed to put a compact ‘flyrig’ together and these have done the job wonderfully.

I wanted a watch that would be more suitable in my workshop environment (dust, woodshavings, metal filings etc) that had good features but wasn’t too ‘dressy’. This watch fits the bill well. My only complaint is that the band is very stiff for about an inch either side of the watch. Hopefully this will ease over time.

review_title: So much better than incandescent bulbs!
reviews: Using these in a stove top hood. So much brighter and less heat generated. Hopefully they’re going to last much longer than the fragile incandescent bulbs that we’ve had previously.
I’m using these for trs footswitch applications where a long reach on stage is needed. Cannot rate them for ‘durability’ yet but they’re working great so far!

Initial bite is very good but the flavour fades ridiculously quickly and textures vary from flavour to flavour. Couldn’t chew a piece for more than a couple of minutes and the aftertaste of the cinnamon made me feel quite nauseous about ten minutes after spitting the gum out.
Fits well and offers good protection along with the card storage option. Bought for my teenage daughter who is bery pleased with it.

Bought this to replace one that got broken by one of our dogs pushing through it! So, we’ve liked it enough to replace it with the same model rather than change anything. All the time that (just) our cats were using it, it has worked well. Only real criticism is that the snap-in section that holds the pivots for the flap in place can unclip fairly easily. A couple of drops of CA glue solved that issue.
